OL,3,CLarge flames and plumes of smoke could
OL,4,Cbe seen coming from the building
OL,6,FEmergency services have been tackling
OL,7,Fa large fire at a former social club
OL,8,Fin Wigan.JCrews were called to the
OL,9,Fsite on Northumberland Street in
OL,10,FWhelley on Wednesday 8th April, at
OL,11,Faround 5pm.
OL,13,FLarge flames and plumes of smoke could
OL,14,Fbe seen coming from the building.
