OL,3,CLarge flames and plumes of smoke could
OL,4,Cbe seen coming from the building
OL,6,FA spokesperson for Greater Manchester
OL,7,FFire and Rescue Service (GMFRS) said:
OL,8,F"Shortly before 5pm this afternoon,
OL,9,Fseveral fire engines from across
OL,10,FGreater Manchester were called to
OL,11,Fattend a fire involving a building on
OL,12,FNorthumberland Street, Wigan.
OL,14,F"Crews arrived quickly and used
OL,15,Fseveral hose reels to extinguish the
OL,16,Ffire.
OL,18,F"The incident has now been scaled down
OL,19,Fand crews remain in attendance at this
OL,20,Ftime to ensure the area is safe."
