OL,3,CLarge flames and plumes of smoke could
OL,4,Cbe seen coming from the building
OL,6,FThe building is believed to be the
OL,7,FWhelley Labour Club.
OL,9,FThe fire service says the incident has
OL,10,Fbeen scaled down but crews are still
OL,11,Fat the scene.
OL,13,FPeople are being advised to avoid the
OL,14,Farea.
